# Contributors

This file is part of a **read-only public mirror**. All commits
originate upstream in the private source repository. Contributions
are not accepted in this mirror — see the upstream repo for the
contribution process.

This is a **static informational file**, shipped to the mirror by
`git-filter-repo` like any other allowlisted path. It is refreshed by
hand when desired, by regenerating the filtered `git shortlog -sne`
against the rewritten history (emails are in the
`<localpart>@global-claude-config.local` form). It is no longer
synthesized as a commit on top of filter-repo's output — see
`.github/public-mirror/README.md` and issue #208 for why that change
was made.

